Body: I have answered this kind of question before well let me explain Its not improving your life career. that career meaning "A career is an individual's metaphorical "journey" through learning, work and other aspects of life" In our CareerXon project meaning is for website who have career pages needs to be interconnected to one platform forexample https://www.facebook.com/careers, https://www.toyota-industries.com/careers/ https://www.honda.com/careers etc so on Those companies pages will be connected to one platform which will list all vacancies real time in your respected fields upon search. It will show all relevant field vacancies near you with regarding to your location.  Quote from: szfinx on October 26, 2017, 03:21:14 PM Could you explain briefly why your project need a token apart of fundraising? In return, what are the investors going to receive apart of the token? Token part as described before will be used as a payment processor for skills development for the companies who are looking for a zero fees unified platform.Apart from token this project would not or can't exist as we have past experience in different types of programming fields not a single type programming comes near to the block chain, that much data processing in real time with many websites its impossible without block chain. What investor would get apart from token i would say you will be the first step toward building your future generations careers by providing them a single unified connected system. you can check whitepaper for benefits section,you will get updates every step of the way that's up to you to decide. Thank you so much
